 Feyikemi Abudu and Jola Ayeye are back with a new episode of “I Said What I Said”, a humour-laden socio-cultural commentary podcast. In this episode, the duo let us in on how they spent the last days of 2020, the upsides and not so great sides. Finding new hobbies, going back to the streets and of course Valentine! Watch the video below:   The best Nigerian and African video content from around the web specially curated for YOU! 